Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:26.03,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}mebaeru hana no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:32.29,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}omoi no kakera afurete kuru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:44.97,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}kono te ni moraeta kimi no nukumori
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:53.97,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}takaramono ni naru mirai he michibiite kureta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:23:03.90,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}zutto kimi no koe wo oikaketeita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:09.41,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}itsu kara nan darou tsuyoku natta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.41,0:23:16.50,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}kiiroi sekai sagashita mono wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:24.21,ED Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}tabiji no hate ni kitto mitsukaru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:13.31,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}Po mrazivé vichřici,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:19.44,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}v níž suchý vítr vál,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:26.03,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}se ve mně začínají vytvářet různé pocity,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:32.29,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\blur12}jako v květině, která brzy vykvete.
